# Update Documentation on CLI Changes

When any CLI commands, options, features, or types are added or modified, always update the following documentation files:

1. **README** — `cosmic-cli/README.md`
2. **CLI reference docs** — `cosmic-website/pages/docs/cli.mdx`

## What to update

- New commands or subcommands: add usage examples and descriptions
- New options/flags: document in the relevant command section
- Changed behavior: update descriptions and examples to reflect the new behavior
- New types or interfaces: ensure any user-facing changes are reflected in docs

## Checklist

- [ ] `README.md` updated with new/changed commands and options
- [ ] `cosmic-website/pages/docs/cli.mdx` updated with new/changed commands and options
- [ ] Examples in docs match the current implementation
